    "It is inevitable that substantial information is lost in this transformation.",
    "Citing Bajusz et al.",
    "25, \"despite the generally positive findings about the applicability of the Tanimoto coefficient several of its weaknesses have also been reported from as early as in a 1998 study.\"",
